    <h>tilg</h>
    <p><g>tilg</g>
        <en>throw, cast, toss, fling</en> is a <a href="?xx=verbs/simple_verbs">simple verb</a>.</p>

    <section id="forms">
        <h>forms</h>
        <p>The principal parts of <g>tilg</g> are – <ul>
                <li><m>tilgidh</m> – future independent, i.e. <en>will throw</en></li>
                <li><m>tilg</m> – past independent, i.e. <en>threw</en></li>
                <li><m>tilgeadh</m> – verbal noun, i.e. <en>throwing</en></li>
            </ul>
        </p>
